casebody.data:
Amy McCOMB
v.
Kenneth PHELPS. No. 29P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 4, 2006. Bruce H. Robinson, Jr., Wilmington, for Amy McComb. Ralph Pennington, Wilmington, for Kenneth Phelps.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 20th day of January 2006 by Plaintiff in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 4th day of May 2006."
